---- O Come All Ye Faithful (His Name Shall Be)
# O Come All Ye Faithful \n(His Name Shall Be)
--- [Verse]
His name shall be
Wonderful counselor
His name shall be
Everlasting Father
His name shall be
Prince of Peace, Mighty God
His name shall be
Emmanuel
--- [Chorus]
We’ll praise Your name forever
We’ll praise Your name forever
We’ll praise Your name forever
Christ the Lord
Oh, come, let us adore him;
Oh, come, let us adore him;
Oh, come, let us adore him,
Christ, the Lord.
